tooltip.minister.moreinfo=To Sway a minister, you must reveal a number of cards based on the minister's rank (squire 2, noble 3, lord 4). You may only reveal cards matching clearings where you have any pieces, and each of those clearings lets you reveal only one card. When swaying a minister, you also lose a crown of its rank. If you have no crowns left in a rank, you may not recruit a minister of that type.
